    "description": "你是一只饥饿的老鼠，每天在下水道中四处搜寻残羹冷炙。有一天，你遇到了好心的魔法师“地沟油块”，从此变身成一名强大的小小 Morsel。借助你获得的新力量，出发前往危险的上层世界，与猫军团的镇压大军展开巧妙周旋，一路上收集新的 Morsel，并根据情况有策略地切换游戏角色。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/cf62d540bbb0221963205821abb096a3.poster.avif?t=1769538257\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/cf62d540bbb0221963205821abb096a3.webm?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/cf62d540bbb0221963205821abb096a3.mp4?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>由开发商 Furcula 推出的《Morsels》是一款充满奇妙趣味的俯视角轻肉鸽类怪兽收集游戏，玩家可以随意切换游戏角色。这款游戏充满了各式各样的疯狂招数和角色特征，玩家可以使用魔法卡片变身成小怪兽，收集并培养一群自己的怪兽护卫来对抗猫军团的统治，不惜一切代价坚持生存下去。<br><br>- 使用轮换列表中收集的 Morsel 随时切换角色，与敌人战斗<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/cb2743a9d457d78274b4a883adadfa94.poster.avif?t=1769538257\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/cb2743a9d457d78274b4a883adadfa94.webm?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/cb2743a9d457d78274b4a883adadfa94.mp4?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 每个 Morsel 都有自己的独特能力和优势，它们可能受到疾病的折磨，也可通过强化道具和怪癖提升能力<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/2275cf03952251a610a434df88585371.poster.avif?t=1769538257\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/2275cf03952251a610a434df88585371.webm?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/2275cf03952251a610a434df88585371.mp4?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 提供多个隐藏的奖励关卡，感受特立独行的艺术风格和惊心动魄的游戏体验<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/e922df05a8809bc0cee68e4c620298af.poster.avif?t=1769538257\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/e922df05a8809bc0cee68e4c620298af.webm?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/e922df05a8809bc0cee68e4c620298af.mp4?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 富有吸引力的游戏玩法，让人欲罢不能<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/140f571b309f627236c9ca31928b0276.poster.avif?t=1769538257\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/140f571b309f627236c9ca31928b0276.webm?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719040/extras/140f571b309f627236c9ca31928b0276.mp4?t=1769538257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
